---
const isDev = import.meta.env.DEV;
const mainSiteUrl = isDev ? 'http://localhost:4321' : 'https://newmaybe.com';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <script is:inline>
    (function() {
      const match = document.cookie.match(/theme=(dark|light)/);
      const theme = (match && match[1]) || localStorage.getItem('theme') || (window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches ? 'dark' : 'light');
      document.documentElement.classList.add(theme);
    })();
  </script>
  <title>网页物理交互与感官艺术博物馆 · newmaybe 实验层</title>
  <style>
    @import '@fontsource/cormorant-garamond/latin-400.css';
    @import '@fontsource/cormorant-garamond/latin-400-italic.css';
    @import '@fontsource/cormorant-garamond/latin-600.css';
    @import '@fontsource/noto-serif-sc/chinese-simplified-300.css';
    @import '@fontsource/noto-serif-sc/chinese-simplified-400.css';
    @import '@fontsource/noto-serif-sc/chinese-simplified-500.css';
    @import '@fontsource/noto-serif-sc/chinese-simplified-600.css';

    :root {
      --paper:      #F7F3EC;
      --paper-deep: #EFE9DE;
      --ink:        #2B2722;
      --ink-soft:   #5B5349;
      --ink-faint:  #968B7C;
      --ochre:      #A8643C;
      --line:       #D9CFBF;
      
      --serif-cn: 'Noto Serif SC', 'Songti SC', serif;
      --serif-en: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      :root:not(.light) {
        --paper:      #1E1B18;
        --paper-deep: #262320;
        --ink:        #E8E0D5;
        --ink-soft:   #B5A99A;
        --ink-faint:  #7A7065;
        --ochre:      #C4814E;
        --line:       #3A3430;
      }
    }

    :root.dark {
      --paper:      #1E1B18;
      --paper-deep: #262320;
      --ink:        #E8E0D5;
      --ink-soft:   #B5A99A;
      --ink-faint:  #7A7065;
      --ochre:      #C4814E;
      --line:       #3A3430;
    }

    :root.light {
      --paper:      #F7F3EC;
      --paper-deep: #EFE9DE;
      --ink:        #2B2722;
      --ink-soft:   #5B5349;
      --ink-faint:  #968B7C;
      --ochre:      #A8643C;
      --line:       #D9CFBF;
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    
    body {
      background-color: var(--paper);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: var(--serif-cn), serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgba(168,100,60,0.02) 0%, transparent 45%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 90% 80%, rgba(43,39,34,0.015) 0%, transparent 45%);
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 960px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 3.5rem;
    }

    /* 头部 */
    header {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .back-btn {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--ink-faint);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .back-btn:hover {
      color: var(--ochre);
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }
    .intro {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
      line-height: 1.8;
      max-width: 68ch;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    /* 实验网格 */
    .lab-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(380px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    /* 卡片设计 */
    .lab-card {
      background: var(--paper-deep);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 2.2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      min-height: 260px;
      transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1),
                  box-shadow 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1),
                  border-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .lab-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(43, 39, 34, 0.03);
      border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--ochre) 30%, var(--line));
    }
    :root.dark .lab-card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .card-meta {
      font-family: var(--serif-en), serif;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--ochre);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: block;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .lab-card:hover .card-title {
      color: var(--ochre);
    }

    .card-desc {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .card-foot {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--ink-faint);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      border-top: 1px dashed var(--line);
      padding-top: 1rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .lab-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      body { padding: 3rem 1rem; }
      .container { gap: 2.5rem; }
      .lab-card { padding: 1.6rem; min-height: 220px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <a href={mainSiteUrl} class="back-btn">← 返回主展厅 newmaybe.com</a>
      <h1>物理交互与感官艺术博物馆</h1>
      <p class="intro">这里是 newmaybe 探索网页作为艺术材质的试验场。在这里，网页不只是死板的信息容器，而可以被感知、抚摸、倾听与冥想。在这里找到最解压而优雅的心流瞬间。</p>
    </header>

    <div class="lab-grid">
      <!-- 实验一 -->
      <a href="/zen-writer" class="lab-card">
        <div>
          <span class="card-meta">Exhibit #01 · 沉浸心智</span>
          <h2 class="card-title">禅意写作空间</h2>
          <p class="card-desc">纯净至极的全屏输入白板。内置雨声与风声白噪音，键盘输入时周围控制条自动淡出，让您进入绝对心流的文字创作状态，并支持一键跨域导出。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-foot">
          <span>HTML5 Audio + 沉浸式动效</span>
          <span>开启实验 →</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- 实验二 -->
      <a href="/floating-verse" class="lab-card">
        <div>
          <span class="card-meta">Exhibit #02 · 物理交互</span>
          <h2 class="card-title">随风诗词画布</h2>
          <p class="card-desc">将诗词文字打碎为在夜空中静静漂浮的粒子，鼠标滑过产生平滑物理排斥波动，移开后徐徐聚合重组，隐喻脑海中半成形的灵感流淌。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-foot">
          <span>HTML5 Canvas + 粒子物理引擎</span>
          <span>开启实验 →</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- 实验三 -->
      <a href="/audio-zen" class="lab-card">
        <div>
          <span class="card-meta">Exhibit #03 · 视听冥想</span>
          <h2 class="card-title">视听冥想空间</h2>
          <p class="card-desc">通过磬（Singing Bowl）声释放压力。点击屏幕敲击磬圈，发出空灵正弦泛音，Canvas 实时涟漪扩散，可伴随大自然风雨的呼唤进行呼吸冥想。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-foot">
          <span>Web Audio API + 交互波纹</span>
          <span>开启实验 →</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- 实验四 -->
      <a href="/ink-flow" class="lab-card">
        <div>
          <span class="card-meta">Exhibit #04 · 网页材质</span>
          <h2 class="card-title">水墨生成流体</h2>
          <p class="card-desc">将纸墨香气融入网页流体物理。鼠标拖动会渲染如水墨落于宣纸般的飘散烟雾粒子轨迹，提供墨汁厚度、色调控制与一键清空重绘。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-foot">
          <span>Generative Flow + 流体渲染</span>
          <span>开启实验 →</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
